her they are receiving an acetylcholinesterase inhibitor.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/146644/', '', 'Amisulpride, Cariprazine, Lurasidone', 'Aducanumab', 1767369485);
